      <title>独家：消息人士称，奥地利官员警告 Raiffeisen 不要与俄罗斯寡头交易</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/austrian-officials-warn-off-raiffeisen-russian-oligarch-deal-sources-say-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，奥地利当局因担心美国的强烈反对，敦促瑞夫艾森国际银行（RBI）放弃一项与俄罗斯寡头有关的交易，这对印度央行解救滞留在俄罗斯的资金的计划构成打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/austrian-officials-warn-off-raiffeisen-russian-oligarch-deal-sources-say-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 14:46:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
